#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot User's Manual"
msgstr "LabPlot उपयोक्तृपुस्तिका"

#. Tag: author
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<firstname>Helen</firstname><surname>Faulkner</surname> <contrib>LabPlot man "
"page.</contrib> <email>helen_ml_faulkner@yahoo.co.uk</email>"
msgstr ""
"<firstname>हेलेन</firstname><surname>Faulkner</surname> <contrib>LabPlot man "
"page.</contrib> <email>helen_ml_faulkner@yahoo.co.uk</email>"

#. Tag: date
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "2018-09-28"
msgstr "२०१८-०९-२८"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot 2.6"
msgstr "लैबप्लॉट् २.६"

#. Tag: productname
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot"
msgstr "लैबप्लॉट"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<मन्वोल्नुम्>१</मन्वोल्नुम्>"

#. Tag: refname
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>labplot</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>लबप्लॉट्</refname> इति"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"an application by KDE for interactive graphing and analysis of scientific "
"data."
msgstr ""
"वैज्ञानिकदत्तांशस्य अन्तरक्रियाशीलग्राफिंग् तथा विश्लेषणार्थं KDE द्वारा एकः अनुप्रयोगः।"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>labplot</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>LabPlot options</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>file</replaceable></arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>labplot</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>LabPlot विकल्पाः</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>सञ्चिका</replaceable></"
"arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot is a data plotting and analysis tool."
msgstr "LabPlot इति आँकडा-प्लॉटिङ्ग्-विश्लेषण-उपकरणम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Its features include 2D and 3D data and function plotting, easy editing of "
"plots, analysis of data and functions, support for different worksheets "
"using MDI and LabPlot project files."
msgstr ""
"अस्य विशेषतासु 2D तथा 3D डाटा तथा फंक्शन् प्लॉटिङ्ग्, प्लॉट् इत्यस्य सुलभं सम्पादनं, डाटा तथा "
"फंक्शन्स् इत्यस्य विश्लेषणं, MDI तथा LabPlot परियोजना सञ्चिकानां उपयोगेन भिन्नकार्यपत्राणां "
"समर्थनं च अन्तर्भवति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that LabPlot is called using <command>labplot</command>."
msgstr "ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् LabPlot <command>labplot</command> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन आह्वयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot options"
msgstr "LabPlot विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a full summary of generic options, run <userinput><command>labplot</"
"command> <parameter>--help</parameter></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"सामान्यविकल्पानां पूर्णसारांशाय <userinput><command>labplot</command> <parameter>--"
"help</parameter></userinput> चालयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "--no-splash"
msgstr "--न-स्प्लैश"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not show the splash screen."
msgstr "स्प्लैश स्क्रीन् न दर्शयन्तु।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "--presenter"
msgstr "--प्रस्तोता"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start in the presenter mode."
msgstr "प्रस्तोता मोड् मध्ये आरभत ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "तर्काः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "file"
msgstr "सञ्चिका"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of the project to be opened, usually ending with <literal role="
"\"extension\">.lml</literal>."
msgstr ""
"उद्घाटनीयस्य परियोजनायाः स्थानं, प्रायः <literal role=\"extension\">.lml</"
"literal> इत्यनेन समाप्तं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The project file can be also compressed, with its filename ending with "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.lml.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">."
"lml.bz2</literal> or <literal role=\"extension\">.lml.xz</literal>."
msgstr ""
"परियोजनासञ्चिका अपि संपीडयितुं शक्यते, तस्याः सञ्चिकानाम <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.lml.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.lml.bz2</literal> अथवा "
"<literal role इत्यनेन समाप्तं भवति =\"विस्तार\">.lml.xz</literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "इदमपि पश्यन्तु"

#. Tag: member
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full user documentation is available through the KDE Help Centre. You can "
"also enter the URL <ulink url=\"help:/labplot\">help:/labplot</ulink> "
"(either enter this <acronym>URL</acronym> into &dolphin;, or run "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/labplot</"
"parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"KDE सहायताकेन्द्रस्य माध्यमेन पूर्णं उपयोक्तृदस्तावेजं उपलभ्यते । भवान् <ulink url=\"help:/"
"labplot\">help:/labplot</ulink> इति URL अपि प्रविष्टुं शक्नोति (एतत् <acronym>URL</"
"acronym> इत्येतत् &dolphin; मध्ये प्रविशतु, अथवा <userinput><command>khelpcenter "
"चालयितुं शक्नोति </command> <parameter>सहाय्यम्:/labplot</parameter></userinput>)।"

